"Oh, hello.<br>It's you.":
"I thought I felt
someone else's presence.

"I do want to spend time talking to you
but sadly, I have prior commitments."

"Hm...!　Y-you...
fancy seeing you here."

"I was asked, to form a party
with him."

"...hmm, being denied
with such force, that

"Okay okay, I understand.
